---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: DeBitpay Directory - Alternative places to spend Bitcoin without BitPay
description: DeBitpay Directory lets you find places to spend Bitcoin without BitPay by recommending alternatives to places accepting Bitcoin via BitPay that you already know.
---

{% set placeslist = collections.places %}

{# <h1>This is global data: {{siteData.name}}</h1> #}

<main role="main" id="places">
  <section class="jumbotron text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <svg class="logo" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="160" height="160" viewBox="0 0 120 120" version="1.1"  xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xml:space="preserve" xmlns:serif="http://www.serif.com/" style="fill-rule:evenodd;clip-rule:evenodd;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-miterlimit:2;"><path d="M26.266,25.016l35.897,-22.016l-3.966,16.547c27.965,11.077 35.418,34.734 34.597,56.409c-6.872,-16.957 -19.764,-27.046 -40.447,-32.003l-4.065,16.96l-22.016,-35.897Z" style="fill-rule:nonzero;"/><path d="M53.127,52.877l1.346,-5.511c4.582,1.256 9.1,2.951 13.321,5.137l-2.577,11.021c1.35,-0.69 2.55,-1.22 3.9,-1.61c3.781,-1.365 7.985,-1.24 11.656,0.098c5.227,5.446 8.342,12.295 11.157,19.194c-0.017,4.532 -0.996,9.152 -2.638,13.186c-5.805,14.017 -18.667,22.303 -33.3,22.548c-5.706,0.381 -12.11,-0.55 -17.25,-2.674l14.385,-61.389m2.49,51.563l6.45,-27.656c1.2,-1.13 2.475,-1.965 3.975,-2.365c1.094,-0.347 2.229,-0.629 3.375,-0.675c1.068,-0.043 3.634,0.073 4.908,0.892c2.481,1.596 2.919,6.005 2.742,8.647c-0.505,7.568 -3.404,14.793 -10.125,18.976c-3.431,2.262 -7.527,2.512 -11.325,2.181"/></svg>
      <h1 class="jumbotron-heading">
        DeBitpay Directory
      </h1>
      <p class="lead text-muted">
        Wanted to buy something with Bitcoin, but the merchant uses BitPay (<a href="{{ '/anti-bitcoin/' | url }}">anti-Bitcoin service</a>)? Find alternatives accepting Bitcoin without it.
      </p>
      <p>
        <input class="search form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="Type a merchant name..." />
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="album py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <ul class="row list">
        {% for item in placeslist %}
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <a class="card-link" href="{{ item.url | url }}">
              <div class="card mb-4 box-shadow">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">{{ item.data.title }}</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Find alternatives to {{ item.data.description | uncapitalize | openSentence }} without BitPay.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>

      <p class="lead text-muted text-center">
        Do you know of a merchant accepting Bitcoin via BitPay that's not included here? Tag them on Twitter with hashtag #DeBitpay. Or <a href="https://github.com/alexk111/DeBitpay-Directory/issues" target="_blank">post an issue on GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<script src="/scripts/index.js"></script>
